 •A multi-vehicle collision occured early this morning between the Middelburg Toll Plaza and the weighbridge. TRAC Media spokesperson, Ms Solange Nicholson confirmed that three people were killed and one critically injured in the collision. The multi-vehicle accident near the Middelburg toll plaza. An investigation to determine the cause of the accident is currently underway.  •In a seperate incident, yet another accident occurred this morning on the N4 between the Hendrina and Woestalleen offramps. It has been confirmed that the accident involved a single vehicle wherein one person was killed. A Corsa Lite lost control and collided with the barricades on the side of the highway. The victims have yet to be identified.      One dead in early morning crash Fake notes in Belfast leads to two arrests Theft of motor vehicles on the rise Accident claims the life of an infant • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za